-- Lanxess CEO Heitmann Buys 275,000 Euros of Shares, Focus Reports
-- B y   A l e x   W e b b
-- 2012-04-15T13:50:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-15/lanxess-ceo-heitmann-buys-275-000-euros-of-shares-focus-reports.html
Lanxess AG (LXS)  Chief Executive Officer
Axel Heitmann bought 275,000 euros ($360,000) worth of stock in
the company, bringing his total since January to 1.9 million
euros,  Focus  reported.  Heitmann made the purchase of 4,780 shares on Tuesday,
Focus reported in an e-mailed preview of an article to be
published tomorrow, without saying where it got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
